avdta.project

Class SAVProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.project.Project
      • avdta.project.TransitProject
        • avdta.project.DemandProject
          • avdta.project.SAVProject

  • public class SAVProject
extends DemandProject
    This represents an SAV project. This adds a fleet file and identifiers associating the project with SAVs.
